00:47:34.530 --> 00:47:37.750
of not just ideas, but
relationships between people.

00:47:37.750 --> 00:47:39.370
Whether that's
customers and producers

00:47:39.370 --> 00:47:42.750
or whether it's producers
and supply chain and workers.

00:47:42.750 --> 00:47:44.430
And what the intangible
economy is doing

00:47:44.430 --> 00:47:45.690
