have no regulations at all.

00:49:09.430 --> 00:49:12.030
But it may be that some
combination of ICT,

00:49:12.030 --> 00:49:15.060
just the general
trajectory of capitalism,

00:49:15.060 --> 00:49:17.803
and the regulatory,
the political economy,

00:49:17.803 --> 00:49:19.386
might have been
driving that increase.

00:49:19.386 --> 00:49:20.585
We don't know.

